---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Jeremy Craig Saunders">
  <section class="md:min-h-[80vh] flex md:items-center bg-[#1A3C2F]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-8 md:pt-0">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="w-full max-w-sm md:max-w-md md:w-5/12 lg:w-4/12 opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_1s_ease-in_forwards]">
          <img src="/assets/images/about.JPG" alt="Jeremy Craig Saunders" class="rounded-3xl w-full h-auto object-cover aspect-[3/4] object-top shadow-2xl" />
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-6/12 flex flex-col mt-4 md:mt-0">
          <p class="text-[#E5C8A6] text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed mb-8 opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_1s_ease-in_0.3s_forwards]">
            I'm Jeremy Craig Saunders, a musician and producer based in Sydney, Australia. My journey in music began at an early age, and I've dedicated my life to crafting sounds that move people.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-[#8B7355] text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8 opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_1s_ease-in_0.6s_forwards]">
            My work spans across various genres, but I'm particularly known for blending electronic elements with organic sounds to create unique sonic landscapes. Whether I'm in the studio producing or performing live, my goal is to create memorable experiences through music.
          </p>

          <p class="text-[#8B7355] text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_1s_ease-in_0.9s_forwards]">
            When I'm not making music, you can find me collaborating with other artists, exploring new sound design techniques, or simply getting inspired by the world around me.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style> 